1. *Divno* je otići u šetnju u park. (It's wonderful to go for a walk in the park.)

2. *Divno* je biti u društvu prijatelja. (It's great to be in the company of friends.)

3. Imali smo *divan* vikend. (We had a wonderful weekend.)

4. *Divno* je biti voljen. (It's great to be loved.)

5. Primili smo *divnu* vest od njega. (We received wonderful news from him.)

6. *Divno* je biti ovde sa tobom. (It's wonderful to be here with you.)

7. On je napravio *divan* poklon za nju. (He made a wonderful gift for her.)

8. Ovo je *divan* dan. (It's a beautiful day.)